{"tid":774625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學者：古朝鮮文明5000年歷史　先於黃河文明","createTime":"2018-08-10T12:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:52:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"584042d7c528b1058d554cc456f4072164dc9540","tid":774625,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:54:46.000Z","msg":"亞歐非新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n08月10日(五) 14:15   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20180810/photo/bkn-20180810141520330-0810_00912_001_01p.jpg?20180810144532\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20180810%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180810141520330-0810_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20180810144532&h=4ff8b2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慎鏞廈（小圖）主張古朝鮮文明的歷史比黃河文明悠久。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n南韓社會史學家、首爾大學名譽教授慎鏞廈最近出版新書，提出古朝鮮文明早過有3700年歷史的黃河文明出現，不但是東方文明之源，更與美索不達米亞文明及埃及文明齊名，合稱世界3大古文明。有關說法引起中韓兩地網民熱議，南韓輿論認為慎鏞廈的主張太大膽。 <br />\n<br />\n《朝鮮日報》周三（8日）報道，研究古朝鮮歷史的慎鏞廈在新書《古朝鮮文明的社會史》指出，古朝鮮文明起源於5000年前的大同江流域及遼東地區。大約1.2萬年前，古朝鮮半島出現農耕文化，並成功栽培稻子及豆子，是「世界上最早的」。至新石器時代，農業革命令人口增多，部分人移居北方，位於遼河以東的是穢族，以西則是貊族。 <br />\n<br />\n由於氣候異常持續，遼西的貊族於5000年前向東南遷移，在大同江流域與韓族結合，成為以青銅器文化為基礎的古朝鮮。古朝鮮於1000年後把首都遷往遼東並擴大領土，成立包含朝鮮半島、滿洲、沿海州的一個古代聯邦國家。在整合韓族、穢族、貊族的語言後，出現古朝鮮語，慎鏞廈指這是烏拉爾－阿爾泰語系中，歷史最悠久的語言。 <br />\n<br />\n對於慎鏞廈的主張，有南韓網民聲言也要把黃河文明納入古朝鮮文化之中，但有網民質疑連南韓建國70年歷史都搞不清楚的民族，「去找古朝鮮的歷史做甚麼」。相反，中國網友沒有太大反應，有人笑稱「南韓等於萬國起源」、「有了朝鮮文明才能有整個地球」。"},{"pid":"277b092ebce411e802b6161b7970e0b89550e775","tid":774625,"uid":155079,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"大陸佬同韓狗差唔多樣<br />\n應該係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f5d2f496269dfb2f6703bbaf1db087defcc862","tid":774625,"uid":82628,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"中國自古以來是朝鮮的一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e198ea1219646a33d71c0d5faa6b94045f8568","tid":774625,"uid":144001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"是但啦都係垃圾"},{"pid":"93c46363a89c6d59fc61bad7f3c21dfaa5f8139c","tid":774625,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"韓泡發明了宇宙"},{"pid":"e8d17cb1cc8246023a6aa09602a9ed0f99b7e607","tid":774625,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:00:45.000Z","msg":"在宇宙大爆發前朝鮮早已存在"},{"pid":"193ec606281358a196678b9803b09ce14d765e16","tid":774625,"uid":161935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:05:38.000Z","msg":"朝鮮同中國一樣，都係會搵歷史打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbed973d8e646f3e6921e37e752e58a23ba38fb","tid":774625,"uid":2923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"全世界都係朝鮮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f0c54bb13fd8a19d4e7ba8be21871e63101947","tid":774625,"uid":161945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"朝鮮同支那一撚樣"},{"pid":"8c731ff1dca19912dedab93bcaca32b98dd46071","tid":774625,"uid":41963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/120442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F120442_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3d1bcd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/120449_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F120449_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f32ae6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/120456_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih